  <summary date="2022-05-23T12:48:34Z" status="Introduced in House">Unmask Our Kids Act

This bill prohibits a local educational agency (LEA) from receiving federal funds unless (1) in-person instruction is available to all students at each public elementary and secondary school under the jurisdiction of the LEA, and (2) a parent of a student at any school may opt out of a student face covering requirement.</summary>
